elements.name: As a user I want to create tag

steps.name: I enter "l.solier@uniandes.edu.co" into input field having name attribute "identification"
I enter "Lui$$olier15" into input field having name attribute "password"
I click on element having css selector "button.login"
I click on element having xpath "//a[@href='#/tags/']"
I click on element having xpath "//a[@href='#/tags/new/']"
I enter "Tag kraken" into input field having name attribute "name"
I enter "Slug kraken" into input field having name attribute "slug"
I enter "Descripcion de una tag utilizando Kraken" into input field having name attribute "description"
I enter "Meta title Kraken" into input field having name attribute "metaTitle"
I enter "Meta descripcion Kraken" into input field having name attribute "metaDescription"
I click on element having xpath "//button[span/text()='Save']"
I click on element having xpath "//a[@href='#/tags/']"
